metadata.name: J2 Synth Head #1
metadata.description: The Synth Heads series imagines a world where synthesizers come alive after the creators go to bed. Synth Heads forms a narrative in which each generative collectible is a unique character all its own. The characters are B0B Lynn Pauline Oscar Seq-Ee and Dax 7. Owning a Junction 2 Synth Head comes with a special set of perks that extend beyond art. This limited collection dives deper into what is possible IRL; festival access unlocking future utility in the Beatport/J2 ecosystem and beyond as well as future NFT and metaverse experiences.
